{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"266479-book-of-bhoots","title":"幽魂之书","description":"在这个无月的夜晚，谁在风中窃窃私语？也许什么都没有。也许有事。翻开这本书的页面，也许您会听到。而且，如果您这样做了，那就没有回头路了。","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"3","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Edith Tan"],"illustrators":["Ruchi  Bakshi"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/266479-book-of-bhoots"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/723696/size3/e0ce37ed7c3c01ca31cf9fd159adcc8b.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/723696/size6/e0ce37ed7c3c01ca31cf9fd159adcc8b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158971/size6/03f82e677a47ea2abf3462b113ebd85b.jpg","text":"在这个漆黑无月的夜晚，是谁在外面徘徊呢？\n是谁从树梢呼啸而过，在风中低语地念着你的名字呢？","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158972/size6/c9e4f73e2bc00d81c62c0a749a1039f7.jpg","text":"也许它根本不存在。\n也许它真的存在着。\n这取决于你的所在地。\n这取决于你的信念。","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158973/size6/77751b924f81c2b42108ef2476ef1d6c.jpg","text":"请多留意池塘和河流。\n巴克就居住在这里。\n巴克的手臂和腿都是卷曲的，\n而它的眼睛和嘴巴都长在肚子上。\n巴克","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158974/size6/3670058f6a43d2518b121518bb608ff8.jpg","text":"如果你遇见巴克，请不要担心。\n比起吓唬你，它对偷窃生鱼更感兴趣。\n吧唧\n吧唧\n吧唧","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158975/size6/49741f3d594e5b76f9af6875a0899d2c.jpg","text":"千万不要在夜里抬头仰望天空。\n吉拉亚会像一只鸟一样飞翔在夜空中。\n阳光普照的时候，它就会入睡。\n吉拉亚","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158979/size6/89c6ad32107fbb1bec86c5a53003fd8a.jpg","text":"如果你遇见吉拉亚，不要让它听到你的名字。\n它会吸你的血。\n咕嘟 咕嘟 咕嘟","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158980/size6/8bfe31d98214aef35dc98a9c48dffb16.jpg","text":"看见棕榈树的时候，千万要小心。\n那是雅克轼居住的地方。\n它在空中漂浮着，\n而且它总是很口渴。\n它会把受害者带回家。\n到了第二天，它的树下就会出现骨头。\n雅克轼","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158981/size6/14ebd1a5ac9f386282400fe56673990f.jpg","text":"如果你遇见雅克轼，\n告诉它不要到家里来做客。\n呼哧\n呼哧\n呼哧","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158982/size6/83c239927fcfe4a3482413150bf8dc6b.jpg","text":"行走在铁轨旁的时候，你要非常小心。\n舍恩斗卡达就在这里徘徊。\n它在一种非常可怕的情况下，失去了它的头部。 哎哟!\n它正在寻找着它遗失的东西。\n舍恩斗卡达","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158983/size6/4b397870418777caaf9bc79164813e67.jpg","text":"如果你遇见舍恩斗卡达，\n它会要求你帮它寻找它的头部。\n吜\n吜\n吜","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158984/size6/e5945fff91635390595e4232fef391ae.jpg","text":"要小心迷雾山脉。\n兰塔斯在这里施展了巫术。\n它的脚趾甲很长。它的长发已经触碰到它的膝盖了。它的脚掌是向后扭曲的。\n兰塔斯","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158985/size6/bebd7e110c42a7f3cdac31147b3c74c4.jpg","text":"如果你遇见兰塔斯，千万不要跟随它。\n否则，你再也回不来了。\n怦怦\n怦怦\n怦怦","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158986/size6/d8958a71b9ca48be03a58ab0e80453e2.jpg","text":"到了沙漠，要随时保持警惕。雷特若披莪就隐藏在这里。它使用沙子来改变自己的容貌。今天它也许是一座棕色的山丘，明天它可能是沙滩上的一条波痕。\n雷特若披莪","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158987/size6/5e0bbce92daa41a4c804ac6c83a16f2a.jpg","text":"如果你去到了沙漠，请不要穿棕色和黄色的衣服。这个沙子妖怪会攻击你。\n嘶\n嘶\n嘶","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158988/size6/251af41b30ba6cef08772f89bd7b4644.jpg","text":"请远离在森林里移动着的灯火。\n科尔利戴瓦就潜伏在这里。\n它拿着火炬，彻夜跳舞和骚扰旅客。\n科尔利戴瓦","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158989/size6/20ef779b682c483ee61d71e2e6e644bf.jpg","text":"如果有一只隐形的手试图要点亮你的灯，那么你就大声尖叫，然后逃跑。\n哧溜 哧溜 哧溜","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158990/size6/4a9cbb1be27a354a264e35b3d8a61bfd.jpg","text":"在这个黑夜里，究竟是谁在你的窗外嚎叫呢？\n你来决定吧！","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158991/size6/e987cb992d48c95bc4134eba4a87f3c4.jpg","text":"也许是一只会吸血的鸟。\n也许是一位脚掌向后扭曲的女人。\n也许是一阵愤怒的风。","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158992/size6/ed5181b584558609fd9c48d0aae75ae0.jpg","text":"舍恩斗卡达 - 西孟加拉邦\n巴克 - 阿萨姆邦\n兰塔斯 - 克什米尔\n雷特若披莪 - 拉贾斯坦邦\n科尔利戴瓦 - 卡纳塔克邦\n雅克轼 - 喀拉拉邦\n印度鬼图\n吉拉亚 - 比哈尔邦","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":19,"words":98}}